N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 22.6 - Supplies provided

State Regulations

The commissioner shall prepare all forms, directions and
examinations, and perform such other official duties as may be necessary to
carry out the provisions of the Election Law relative to certificates of
literacy. He shall send such supplies to superintendents of schools, for use at
local registration, and to county boards of elections, for use at central
registration, on or before October 1st of each year. Notes
